iaik.tc.tss.api.structs.tpm
Interface TcITpmKey

All Known Subinterfaces:
TcITpmKeyNew
All Known Implementing Classes:
TcTpmKey, TcTpmKey12, TcTpmKey12New, TcTpmKeyNew
public interface TcITpmKey

This class is a common interface for TcTpmKey (1.1 TPM Spec) and TcTpmKey12 (1.2 TPM Spec). This interface has no functionality. It's only purpose is that it is used in TSS functions where both, TcTpmKey and TcTpmKey12 can be passed as arguments.
